{"tid":477852,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴打好鍾意搭車叫有落","createTime":"2017-11-23T12:05:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-24T04:30:52.000Z","uid":147527,"like":14,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"995e964d005a83b30f80596572c75357c6946521","tid":477852,"uid":147527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T12:05:20.000Z","msg":"次次上車都好撚期待落車<br />\n因為每次最後一段直路<br />\n都可以大大聲咁叫：「轉彎，有落！」<br />\n個語氣就好似董昭咁，董昭，先，行告退<br />\n嚇撚到全車人都望撚住我<br />\n成個氣勢即刻昇華到一朝天子<br />\n跟住就好撚型咁慢慢行落車<br />\n沿途見到啲人帶住景仰既眼神望住朕<br />\n大地在我腳下，國計置於手中<br />\n朕之江山美好如畫<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FfBGSBF6tSk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFfBGSBF6tSk&d=Vj677ZQh3BTuz5Y4znqgEDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=3cd629f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FfBGSBF6tSk</a>"},{"pid":"84d658f9e72ea6c3e91422cae2070df05289ff82","tid":477852,"uid":147527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T12:15:32.000Z","msg":"哪個再敢多說話？"},{"pid":"239d35fb3cce2ed298225e8c69d32ecd9e308b69","tid":477852,"uid":147527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T12:18:17.000Z","msg":"夷平六國是誰"},{"pid":"01863e3d7e0c8ba10262e00d94a03f731a2630ef","tid":477852,"uid":147527,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T12:21:50.000Z","msg":"屌點解會係達哥版黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n哪個統一稱霸"},{"pid":"567cb3e546d146e12fa3c5b5df0c6998dc58905e","tid":477852,"uid":61463,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T12:33:39.000Z","msg":"我搭地鐵都會咁叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a868f20c090f4f3a40dc28e02a36a0da4185b69","tid":477852,"uid":1374,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T12:44:30.000Z","msg":"我自己揸車都會"},{"pid":"a138eedde4e17df0f676d4351958bd3b8f06a35d","tid":477852,"uid":147527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"